{"tid":1902062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡宣布總理在內等高層官員全體減薪 前線醫護增發獎金！","createTime":"2020-02-28T07:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T11:19:39.000Z","uid":63113,"like":331,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"c17879c7609669cea56b66be3f2ed3ce0d4cb442","tid":1902062,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d01a09a6c2d74a52383f76c1e3b8121ae24a13","tid":1902062,"uid":35456,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1076060de9415669549dc6d6a65afcc6261c0cee","tid":1902062,"uid":63113,"like":134,"dislike":3,"score":131,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:05:43.000Z","msg":"新加坡政府宣布，為了與國民在疫情下共渡時艱，總理等全體內閣成員，減薪一個月；國會議員削減一個月津貼；資深公務員減薪半個月。總統哈莉瑪亦跟隨減薪一個月。此外，所有前線醫護人員，都可以獲得相當於1個月薪金，作為獎金。<br />\n<br />\n副總理兼財長王瑞杰說，政府高層集體減薪，是要展現新加坡團結，政治領導者要盡其所能，幫助社會渡過難關。他又感謝前線醫護人員，在未知的疫症戰爭中犧牲，發放獎金是政府對他們的最實際支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1269845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1269845&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=940df1a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1269845</a>"},{"pid":"c344ed6bb7ce3bdfdcd9d717a2e4f8a78d57568b","tid":1902062,"uid":76310,"like":125,"dislike":4,"score":121,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"777: 我地要全體加人工"},{"pid":"5ef69022b04a7682ccebd473ed849785b6408c7b","tid":1902062,"uid":255637,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"港共 : Am i a joke to you ?"},{"pid":"3d879b54e34bf3918ca27cbab8212c0ea4405148","tid":1902062,"uid":51271,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"香港: 狗加人工，醫護cut b