r />\n如果柒蛾可以做到坡佬一半<br />\n我相信到依家大把人仲海底撈緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無計，中共專養廢物同狗"},{"pid":"bf2371971e468ba127dbf6accd5d4a04716d159f","tid":1902062,"uid":35270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"成日話人極權國家<br />\n根本香港政府垃圾都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【總結財政預算案2020】副總理王瑞傑：總統、總理與所有部長將減薪一個月</strong><br />\n<br />\n副總理兼財政部長王瑞傑今午（28日）宣佈，所有部長將減薪一個月，與國人一同渡過這段艱難時期。這將包括總理和副總理等。哈莉瑪總統也表示將減薪一個月。<br />\n<br />\n他是在國會總結新財年政府財政政策辯論宣佈這項消息，除了部長，國會議員也將減少一個月的津貼，一些高級公務員也會減薪半個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/budget2020-dpm-announces-paycut-ministers-1057561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fbudget2020-dpm-announces-paycut-ministers-1057561&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=b253188e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/budget2020-dpm-announces-paycut-ministers-1057561</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【總結財政預算案2020】王瑞傑：抗疫前線人員將額外獲得多達一個月特別花紅</strong><br />\n<br />\n協助對抗2019冠狀病毒抗疫情的前線人員將額外獲得多達一個月的特別花紅，以肯定他們的付出和貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n副總理兼財政部長王瑞傑在國會總結新財政年財政預算案辯論時，宣佈這個消息。受惠的包括衛生部和政府醫院的醫護人員，以及其他前線機構直接參與抗炎的人員。其他在對抗疫情方面有顯著貢獻的公務員，也會得到適當的肯定。<br />\n<br />\n此外，王瑞傑也宣佈，為900家公共衛生防範診所提供一次性的2019冠狀病毒津貼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/budget2020-special-bonus-for-frontline-1057601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fbudget2020-special-bonus-for-frontline-1057601&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=17783513\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/budget2020-special-bonus-for-frontline-1057601</a>"},{"pid":"17f6d587ad071a9b88b69da6d5b8a55494a0d9ec","tid":1902062,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"goodjob"},{"pid":"7638da7e401b79fa0c47198b47c88b8d60a7b723","tid":1902062,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"支那同新加坡都係主權國家, 但看待人民既本心係完全唔同"},{"pid":"7575202c22269eba855c5bf4e9b2f66be86a0d66","tid":1902062,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"新加坡又贏"},{"pid":"fc2580dfe68d6d13d863db0cc96bf22b61f5a10a","tid":1902062,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca54131fdc5c598b7b2f929143c64c0b4a2cbc8","tid":1902062,"uid":46213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"777: 醫護會自動歸位既 洗鬼加咩 死左咪算囉 引入祖國專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a73795cd314fe9806cd4a07e15255f435a41efe","tid":1902062,"uid":35315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7172f9bba2f8fbb6ba6a0cf804b7b0f8ddbd9ae9","tid":1902062,"uid":57674,"like":95,"dislike":3,"score":92,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:06:37.000Z","msg":"玻佬係仆街係串係獨裁<br />\n但你睇下人 再望下我地自己班高官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"佢地做得叻太多<br />\n最基本係令人民生活得好, 自然唔會有大批人反佢依個政府, 咁佢地就可以永續落去, 但支那政府既人拎住外國護照, 咁仲會有心想支那人民好? 唔好玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd6ff8ea6561ce201f2222163315a64553e958f","tid":1902062,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"死大陸仔，你唔怪得香港人反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有本事繼續硬碰硬，一於睇下邊個傷d"},{"pid":"a9c562e843eda6bdf8a77c64be843fcc74a85c55","tid":1902062,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d69e7955352316ba4cd0d9bb35bf02ff1a1b283","tid":1902062,"uid":231766,"like":0,"dislike